<ul style="list-style-type: square ;"><h2><li><u>Joint Use of Defence Airfield under RCS Udan Scheme<br></u></li></h2><h3><i>IAF has been actively interacting with MoCA/ AAI for sharing its airports and airspace for supporting the increased demands of civil aviation. Accordingly, seven more defence airfields have been opened for joint useto accommodate civil scheduled flights as part of RCS UDAN Scheme in last one year. Scheduled flight operations have commenced from Darbhanga airfield from 08 Nov 20. 39 IAF bases & 7 ALGs have been made available for joint user operations.</i></h3></ul>
